    "ai-tha-ap409:28.2_0": "aspiring to the aggregates,",
    "ai-tha-ap409:28.3_0": "they will serve you",
    "ai-tha-ap409:28.4_0": "lovely,",
    "ai-tha-ap409:29.1_0": "There were sixty chariots,",
    "ai-tha-ap409:29.2_0": "adorned with all our jewellery.",
    "ai-tha-ap409:29.3_0": "Both wavering up,",
    "ai-tha-ap409:29.4_0": "stripped, and gone beyond.",
    "ai-tha-ap409:30.1_0": "on villages, towns, and capital cities,",
    "ai-tha-ap409:30.2_0": "I could stand with my head.",
