    "ai-tha-ap409:32.4_0": "Wearing jeweled earrings",
    "ai-tha-ap409:33.1_0": "But I’m not enough to laugh,",
    "ai-tha-ap409:33.2_0": "of the dimension of neither perception nor non-perception.",
    "ai-tha-ap409:33.3_0": "Associate with the virtuous,",
